reviewText: Absolutely outstanding series, particularly if you have any sense of history or just enjoy a great mystery...a definite recommendation!!!
The North American version was released on November 10, 2015: Foyle's War: The Complete Saga

I purchased this item thinking that it was compatible with US standards.  I was disappointed to learn, upon attempting to play a cd, that the system is compatible with UK standards ONLY.  SUGGESTION:  Groups the CD's by system compatibility, rather than your random practice.
